nhc_headline: ...NARDA EXPECTED TO BECOME A HURRICANE ON TUESDAY...
summary: ...NARDA EXPECTED TO BECOME A HURRICANE ON TUESDAY... As of 3:00 PM CST Mon Sep 22 the center of Narda was located near 16.2, -103.9 with movement WNW at 13 mph. The minimum central pressure was 997 mb with maximum sustained winds of about 60 mph.
